          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Flexibility in Family Sentencing Act of 2016</b></p> <p>This bill amends the federal criminal code to authorize pre-judgment probation for a pregnant or postpartum woman who: (1) commits a specified low-level offense, and (2) is an addict.</p> <p> The conditions of probation must require participation in a court-approved drug treatment program and periodic medical evaluations.</p>]]></text>
          <updateDate>2016-07-14T04:00:00Z</updateDate>
          <name>Introduced in House</name>
        </item>
